{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775848520919,"sessionID":"ses_287309294ffetYBdBvl9AcZJkI","part":{"id":"prt_d78d1f84d001jkB4TkPx7ld8eI","messageID":"msg_d78d1e4fe001EXvmoalHahrP80","sessionID":"ses_287309294ffetYBdBvl9AcZJkI","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_deedbf1ed1b14d17b1889233","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-018/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-018/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器 — Tasks\n2: \n3: > **Module:** pkg/agentd\n4: > **Language:** Go\n5: > **Size:** S\n6: > **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n7: > **Reference:** `changes/AR-018/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-018/design.md`, `changes/AR-018/delta-spec.md`\n8: \n9: ## T1. 定义常量 — pkg/workloadmanager/const.go\n10: \n11: - [ ] 1.1 创建 `pkg/workloadmanager/const.go`\n12: - [ ] 1.2 定义 `LastActivityAnnotationKey = \"last-activity-time\"`\n13: - [ ] 1.3 运行 `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` 确认编译通过\n14: \n15: **Verification:** `pkg/workloadmanager/const.go` 存在；`LastActivityAnnotationKey` 值为 `\"last-activity-time\"`；编译零错误\n16: \n17: ---\n18: \n19: ## T2. 定义常量 — pkg/agentd/const.go\n20: \n21: - [ ] 2.1 创建 `pkg/agentd/` 目录\n22: - [ ] 2.2 创建 `pkg/agentd/const.go`\n23: - [ ] 2.3 定义 `SessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute`（带注释说明用途）\n24: - [ ] 2.4 运行 `go build ./pkg/agentd/...` 确认编译通过\n25: \n26: **Verification:** `pkg/agentd/const.go` 存在；`SessionExpirationTimeout` 值为 `15 * time.Minute`；编译零错误\n27: \n28: ---\n29: \n30: ## T3. 实现 Reconciler 结构体和 Reconcile 方法\n31: \n32: - [ ] 3.1 创建 `pkg/agentd/reconciler.go`\n33: - [ ] 3.2 导入依赖：`context`, `time`, `sandboxv1alpha1`（`sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/api/v1alpha1`）, `errors`（`k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/api/errors`）, `runtime`（`k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime`）, `ctrl`（`sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime`）, `client`（`sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/client`）, `workloadmanager`（内部包）\n34: - [ ] 3.3 定义 `Reconciler` 结构体，嵌入 `client.Client`，字段 `Scheme *runtime.Scheme`\n35: - [ ] 3.4 实现 `Reconcile(ctx context.Context, req ctrl.Request) (ctrl.Result, error)` 方法，完整算法：\n36:   - `sandbox := &sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{}`；`r.Get(ctx, req.NamespacedName, sandbox)`\n37:   - `errors.IsNotFound(err)` → `return ctrl.Result{}, nil`\n38:   - 其他 Get 错误 → `return ctrl.Result{}, err`\n39:   - 读取 `sandbox.Annotations[workloadmanager.LastActivityAnnotationKey]`\n40:   - 注解缺失或为空 → `return ctrl.Result{}, nil`\n41:   - `time.Parse(time.RFC3339, lastActivityStr)`，解析错误 → `return ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: 30s}, err`\n42:   - `expirationTime := lastActivity.Add(SessionExpirationTimeout)`\n43:   - `time.Now().After(expirationTime)` 为 true：\n44:     - `r.Delete(ctx, sandbox)`，错误且非 `IsNotFound` → `return ctrl.Result{}, err`\n45:     - `return ctrl.Result{}, nil`\n46:   - 否则 → `return ctrl.Result{RequeueAfter: time.Until(expirationTime)}, nil`\n47: - [ ] 3.5 运行 `go build ./pkg/agentd/...` 确认编译通过\n48: \n49: **Verification:** `reconciler.go` 编译通过；Reconcile 方法覆盖 delta-spec §Requirement: Reconcile algorithm completeness 全部 10 个步骤\n50: \n51: ---\n52: \n53: ## T4. 实现 SetupWithManager 方法\n54: \n55: - [ ] 4.1 在 `pkg/agentd/reconciler.go` 中实现 `SetupWithManager(mgr ctrl.Manager) error` 方法\n56: - [ ] 4.2 方法体：`return ctrl.NewControllerManagedBy(mgr).For(&sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox{}).Complete(r)`\n57: - [ ] 4.3 运行 `go build ./pkg/agentd/...` 确认编译通过\n58: \n59: **Verification:** `SetupWithManager` 方法签名与 design.md §4.2 一致；编译零错误\n60: \n61: ---\n62: \n63: ## T5. 单元测试 — Reconcile 核心路径覆盖\n64: \n65: - [ ] 5.1 创建 `pkg/agentd/reconciler_test.go`\n66: - [ ] 5.2 定义测试辅助：\n67:   - `newTestScheme() *runtime.Scheme`：创建包含 `sandboxv1alpha1` 的 Scheme\n68:   - `newFakeReconciler(objects ...runtime.Object) *agentd.Reconciler`：使用 `fake.NewClientBuilder` 构建\n69:   - `newSandbox(ns, name string, annotations map[string]string) *sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox`：构造测试 Sandbox\n70: - [ ] 5.3 测试 `TestReconcile_SandboxNotFound`：fake client 中无 Sandbox → `Result{}`, `nil`\n71: - [ ] 5.4 测试 `TestReconcile_GetError`：使用自定义 client wrapper 注入 Get 错误 → `Result{}`, `err`\n72: - [ ] 5.5 测试 `TestReconcile_AnnotationMissing`：Sandbox 无 `last-activity-time` 注解 → `Result{}`, `nil`\n73: - [ ] 5.6 测试 `TestReconcile_AnnotationEmpty`：注解值为 `\"\"` → `Result{}`, `nil`\n74: - [ ] 5.7 测试 `TestReconcile_InvalidTimestamp`：注解值为 `\"not-a-timestamp\"` → `Result{RequeueAfter: 30s}`, `err != nil`\n75: - [ ] 5.8 测试 `TestReconcile_NotExpired`：注解值为 5 分钟前 → `Result{RequeueAfter: ~10m}`, `nil`，Sandbox 未被删除\n76: - [ ] 5.9 测试 `TestReconcile_Expired`：注解值为 20 分钟前 → Sandbox 被删除，`Result{}`, `nil`\n77: - [ ] 5.10 测试 `TestReconcile_DeleteNotFound`：Sandbox 在 Get 和 Delete 之间被删除 → `Result{}`, `nil`\n78: - [ ] 5.11 测试 `TestReconcile_DeleteError`：使用自定义 client wrapper 注入 Delete 错误 → `Result{}`, `err`\n79: - [ ] 5.12 测试 `TestReconcile_AtExpirationBoundary`：注解值恰好 15 分钟前 → `Result{RequeueAfter: >=0}`, `nil`（`After()` 返回 false）\n80: \n81: **Verification:** `go test ./pkg/agentd/... -v -count=1` 全部通过；覆盖 design.md §6.1 测试矩阵全部 10 个场景\n82: \n83: ---\n84: \n85: ## T6. 单元测试 — SetupWithManager\n86: \n87: - [ ] 6.1 测试 `TestSetupWithManager`：使用 envtest 或 fake manager 验证 `SetupWithManager` 返回 `nil` 且无 panic\n88: \n89: **Verification:** `go test ./pkg/agentd/... -run TestSetupWithManager -v` 通过\n90: \n91: ---\n92: \n93: ## T7. 实现 Binary Entry Point — cmd/agentd/main.go\n94: \n95: - [ ] 7.1 创建 `cmd/agentd/` 目录\n96: - [ ] 7.2 创建 `cmd/agentd/main.go`\n97: - [ ] 7.3 定义 `schemeBuilder = runtime.NewScheme()` 和 `setupLog = ctrl.Log.WithName(\"setup\")`\n98: - [ ] 7.4 `init()` 函数：`utilruntime.Must(scheme.AddToScheme(schemeBuilder))` + `utilruntime.Must(sandboxv1alpha1.AddToScheme(schemeBuilder))`\n99: - [ ] 7.5 `main()` 函数：\n100:   - 解析 zap 日志选项：`opts := zap.Options{Development: true}`；`opts.BindFlags(flag.CommandLine)`；`flag.Parse()`\n101:   - `ctrl.SetLogger(zap.New(zap.UseFlagOptions(&opts)))`\n102:   - 构造 Manager：`ctrl.NewManager(ctrl.GetConfigOrDie(), ctrl.Options{Scheme: schemeBuilder, Metrics: metricsserver.Options{BindAddress: \"0\"}, HealthProbeBindAddress: \"0\"})`\n103:   - Manager 构造失败 → `setupLog.Error` + `os.Exit(1)`\n104:   - 注册 Reconciler：`(&agentd.Reconciler{Client: mgr.GetClient(), Scheme: mgr.GetScheme()}).SetupWithManager(mgr)`\n105:   - 注册失败 → `setupLog.Error` + `os.Exit(1)`\n106:   - 启动 Manager：`mgr.Start(ctrl.SetupSignalHandler())`\n107:   - 启动失败 → `setupLog.Error` + `os.Exit(1)`\n108: - [ ] 7.6 导入依赖：`flag`, `os`, `runtime`, `utilruntime`, `sandboxv1alpha1`, `ctrl`, `zap`, `metricsserver`, `agentd`（内部包）\n109: - [ ] 7.7 运行 `go build ./cmd/agentd/...` 确认编译通过\n110: \n111: **Verification:** `cmd/agentd/main.go` 编译通过；覆盖 delta-spec §Requirement: Binary entry point 全部 3 个子需求（Scheme 注册、Manager 配置、Controller 注册与启动）\n112: \n113: ---\n114: \n115: ## T8. 依赖管理\n116: \n117: - [ ] 8.1 运行 `go mod tidy` 确保 `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox` 和 `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime` 依赖正确\n118: - [ ] 8.2 确认 `go.mod` 和 `go.sum` 变更合理\n119: \n120: **Verification:** `go mod tidy` 无异常；`go build ./cmd/agentd/... ./pkg/agentd/...` 编译通过\n121: \n122: ---\n123: \n124: ## T9. 代码质量门禁\n125: \n126: - [ ] 9.1 运行 `go build ./pkg/agentd/... ./cmd/agentd/...` 确认编译通过\n127: - [ ] 9.2 运行 `go test ./pkg/agentd/... -v -count=1` 确认全部测试通过\n128: - [ ] 9.3 运行 `go test -race ./pkg/agentd/...` 确认无数据竞争\n129: - [ ] 9.4 运行 `go vet ./pkg/agentd/... ./cmd/agentd/...` 确认无警告\n130: - [ ] 9.5 运行 `go mod tidy` 确认无变更\n131: - [ ] 9.6 确认 `pkg/agentd/` 下每个 `*.go` 文件都有对应的 `*_test.go` 文件\n132: \n133: **Verification:** 以上 6 项全部通过；exit code 均为 0\n134: \n135: ---\n136: \n137: ## Task Dependencies\n138: \n139: ```\n140: T1 ──┐\n141:      ├──→ T3 ──→ T5 ──┐\n142: T2 ──┘     │          │\n143:            ↓          │\n144:            T4 ──→ T6 ─┤\n145:                       │\n146:            T7 ────────┤\n147:                       │\n148:            T8 ────────┤\n149:                       │\n150:                       ↓\n151:                      T9\n152: ```\n153: \n154: **Parallel execution:**\n155: - T1（workloadmanager 常量）和 T2（agentd 常量）可并行\n156: - T3（Reconcile 实现）需 T1 和 T2 完成后开始（依赖两个常量）\n157: - T4（SetupWithManager）需 T3 完成后开始\n158: - T5（Reconcile 测试）需 T3 完成后开始，可与 T6 并行\n159: - T7（binary entry point）需 T3 和 T4 完成后开始\n160: - T8（依赖管理）可与 T5/T6/T7 并行\n161: - T9 为最终门禁，需所有前置任务完成\n162: \n163: ---\n164: \n165: ## Acceptance Criteria\n166: \n167: | # | Criterion | Command |\n168: |---|-----------|---------|\n169: | AC1 | 编译通过 | `go build ./pkg/agentd/... ./cmd/agentd/...` |\n170: | AC2 | 全部测试通过 | `go test ./pkg/agentd/... -v -count=1` |\n171: | AC3 | 无竞态条件 | `go test -race ./pkg/agentd/...` |\n172: | AC4 | 无 lint 警告 | `go vet ./pkg/agentd/... ./cmd/agentd/...` |\n173: | AC5 | Reconcile 覆盖 10 个测试场景 | `go test ./pkg/agentd/... -run TestReconcile -v` |\n174: | AC6 | SetupWithManager 测试通过 | `go test ./pkg/agentd/... -run TestSetupWithManager -v` |\n175: | AC7 | Binary 编译成功 | `go build ./cmd/agentd/...` |\n176: | AC8 | SessionExpirationTimeout = 15min | 代码审查 `pkg/agentd/const.go` |\n177: | AC9 | LastActivityAnnotationKey = \"last-activity-time\" | 代码审查 `pkg/workloadmanager/const.go` |\n178: | AC10 | 依赖清理 | `go mod tidy` 无变更 |\n179: | AC11 | 每个源文件有对应测试文件 | `ls pkg/agentd/*_test.go` |\n\n(End of file - total 179 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器 — Tasks\n\n> **Module:** pkg/agentd\n> **Language:** Go\n> **Size:** S\n> **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n> **Reference:** `changes/AR-018/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-018/design.md`, `changes/AR-018/delta-spec.md`\n\n## T1. 定义常量 — pkg/workloadmanager/const.go\n\n- [ ] 1.1 创建 `pkg/workloadmanager/const.go`\n- [ ] 1.2 定义 `LastActivityAnnotationKey = \"last-activity-time\"`\n- [ ] 1.3 运行 `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` 确认编译通过\n\n**Verification:** `pkg/workloadmanager/const.go` 存在；`LastActivityAnnotationKey` 值为 `\"last-activity-time\"`；编译零错误\n\n---\n\n## T2. 定义常量 — pkg/agentd/const.go\n","tru