{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775848522213,"sessionID":"ses_287309294ffetYBdBvl9AcZJkI","part":{"id":"prt_d78d1fd5f001ENyM5LDnRGuApA","messageID":"msg_d78d1e4fe001EXvmoalHahrP80","sessionID":"ses_287309294ffetYBdBvl9AcZJkI","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_b0ac892176f7497a856b3974","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-017/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-017/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-017 — PicoD JWT 中间件 — Tasks\n2: \n3: > **Module:** pkg/picod\n4: > **Language:** Go\n5: > **Size:** S\n6: > **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n7: > **Reference:** `changes/AR-017/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-017/design.md`, `changes/AR-017/delta-spec.md`\n8: \n9: ## T1. 定义认证常量和类型\n10: \n11: - [ ] 1.1 在 `pkg/picod/types.go` 中定义常量 `PublicKeyEnvVar = \"PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY\"`\n12: - [ ] 1.2 在 `pkg/picod/types.go` 中定义常量 `MaxBodySize = 32 << 20`（33554432，即 32 MiB）\n13: - [ ] 1.3 运行 `go build ./pkg/picod/...` 确认编译通过\n14: \n15: **Verification:** 常量值与 delta-spec §Requirement: Constants and configuration 一致；编译零错误\n16: \n17: ---\n18: \n19: ## T2. 实现 AuthManager 结构体和公钥加载\n20: \n21: - [ ] 2.1 创建 `pkg/picod/auth.go`\n22: - [ ] 2.2 定义 `AuthManager` 结构体，字段：`publicKey *rsa.PublicKey`，`mutex sync.RWMutex`\n23: - [ ] 2.3 实现 `newAuthManager() *AuthManager` 私有构造函数，返回空的 `AuthManager` 实例\n24: - [ ] 2.4 实现 `LoadPublicKeyFromEnv() error` 方法：\n25:   - 读取环境变量 `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY`，为空返回 `\"environment variable %s is not set\"`\n26:   - PEM 解码，失败返回 `\"failed to decode PEM block\"`\n27:   - `x509.ParsePKIXPublicKey` 解析，失败返回 `\"failed to parse public key: %w\"`\n28:   - 类型断言为 `*rsa.PublicKey`，非 RSA 返回 `\"public key is not RSA\"`\n29:   - 获取写锁，存储公钥，释放锁\n30: - [ ] 2.5 实现 `checkFatal(err error)` 辅助函数：`err != nil` 时调用 `klog.Fatalf(\"failed to load public key: %v\", err)`\n31: - [ ] 2.6 创建 `pkg/picod/auth_test.go`\n32: - [ ] 2.7 实现测试辅助函数：`generateTestPrivateKey(t) *rsa.PrivateKey`（2048-bit RSA）、`generateTestPublicKey(t) string`（PEM 编码公钥）\n33: - [ ] 2.8 测试 `TestAuthManager_LoadPublicKeyFromEnv_ValidKey`：设置有效 RSA 公钥 → `err == nil`，`publicKey != nil`\n34: - [ ] 2.9 测试 `TestAuthManager_LoadPublicKeyFromEnv_MissingEnv`：环境变量未设置 → `err != nil`，包含 \"not set\"\n35: - [ ] 2.10 测试 `TestAuthManager_LoadPublicKeyFromEnv_InvalidPEM`：环境变量为 `\"not-a-pem-block\"` → `err != nil`，包含 \"failed to decode PEM block\"\n36: - [ ] 2.11 测试 `TestAuthManager_LoadPublicKeyFromEnv_NonRSAKey`：环境变量包含非 RSA 公钥（EC 密钥） → `err != nil`，包含 \"public key is not RSA\"\n37: \n38: **Verification:** `go test ./pkg/picod/... -run TestAuthManager -v` 全部通过；覆盖 delta-spec §Requirement: AuthManager structure and public key loading 全部 4 个场景\n39: \n40: ---\n41: \n42: ## T3. 实现 AuthMiddleware JWT 验证中间件\n43: \n44: - [ ] 3.1 在 `pkg/picod/auth.go` 中实现 `AuthMiddleware() gin.HandlerFunc` 方法\n45: - [ ] 3.2 提取 `Authorization` 请求头，缺失时返回 401：`{\"error\": \"Missing Authorization header\", \"code\": 401, \"detail\": \"JWT token required\"}`\n46: - [ ] 3.3 按空格分割验证 `Bearer <token>` 格式，格式错误返回 401：`{\"error\": \"Invalid Authorization header format\", \"code\": 401, \"detail\": \"Use Bearer <token>\"}`\n47: - [ ] 3.4 调用 `jwt.Parse()` 验证 JWT，KeyFunc 中：\n48:   - 检查签名方法必须为 `*jwt.SigningMethodRSA`，否则返回 `\"unexpected signing method: %v\"`\n49:   - 获取读锁，返回 `am.publicKey`\n50:   - 选项：`jwt.WithExpirationRequired()`、`jwt.WithIssuedAt()`、`jwt.WithLeeway(time.Minute)`\n51: - [ ] 3.5 验证失败（`err != nil || !token.Valid`）返回 401：`{\"error\": \"Invalid token\", \"code\": 401, \"detail\": \"<具体错误>\"}`\n52: - [ ] 3.6 验证通过：`c.Request.Body = http.MaxBytesReader(c.Writer, c.Request.Body, MaxBodySize)`，然后 `c.Next()`\n53: - [ ] 3.7 测试 `TestAuthMiddleware_MissingAuthHeader`：无 Authorization 头 → 401\n54: - [ ] 3.8 测试 `TestAuthMiddleware_MalformedAuthHeader`：`Authorization: \"InvalidFormat\"` → 401\n55: - [ ] 3.9 测试 `TestAuthMiddleware_ValidToken`：有效 RS256 JWT（exp 未来，iat 过去） → 200\n56: - [ ] 3.10 测试 `TestAuthMiddleware_ExpiredToken`：exp 为 5 分钟前 → 401\n57: - [ ] 3.11 测试 `TestAuthMiddleware_NonRSASigningMethod`：HS256 签名的 JWT → 401\n58: - [ ] 3.12 测试 `TestAuthMiddleware_MaxBodySize`：验证通过后 Body 被 MaxBytesReader 包装\n59: \n60: **Verification:** `go test ./pkg/picod/... -run TestAuthMiddleware -v` 全部通过；覆盖 delta-spec §Requirement: AuthMiddleware JWT validation 全部 7 个场景\n61: \n62: ---\n63: \n64: ## T4. Server 集成 — 路由注册与认证中间件应用\n65: \n66: - [ ] 4.1 在 `pkg/picod/server.go` 的 `Server` 结构体中增加 `authManager *AuthManager` 字段\n67: - [ ] 4.2 在 `NewServer(config)` 中：\n68:   - 调用 `newAuthManager()` 创建实例\n69:   - 调用 `authManager.LoadPublicKeyFromEnv()`，失败则 `checkFatal(err)` 终止进程\n70:   - 将 `authManager` 存入 Server 结构体\n71: - [ ] 4.3 在 `registerRoutes()` 中：\n72:   - 创建 `/api` 路由组：`api := s.engine.Group(\"/api\")`\n73:   - 应用中间件：`api.Use(s.authManager.AuthMiddleware())`\n74:   - 注册业务端点到 `/api` 组：`POST /execute`、`POST /files`、`GET /files`、`GET /files/*path`\n75:   - `/health` 端点保持在路由组外：`s.engine.GET(\"/health\", s.HealthCheckHandler)`\n76: - [ ] 4.4 测试 `TestServer_HealthEndpointPublic`：`GET /health` 无 Authorization 头 → 200\n77: - [ ] 4.5 测试 `TestServer_ApiRoutesRequireAuth`：`POST /api/execute` 无 Authorization 头 → 401\n78: - [ ] 4.6 测试 `TestServer_ApiRoutesAcceptValidJWT`：`POST /api/execute` 带有效 JWT → 200\n79: \n80: **Verification:** `go test ./pkg/picod/... -run TestServer -v` 全部通过；覆盖 delta-spec §Requirement: Route protection with AuthMiddleware 全部 3 个场景\n81: \n82: ---\n83: \n84: ## T5. 时钟容差（Leeway）验证\n85: \n86: - [ ] 5.1 测试 `TestAuthMiddleware_ClockLeeway`：JWT 的 exp 设为 30 秒前，iat 设为 30 秒前 → 200（在 1 分钟 leeway 窗口内被接受）\n87: \n88: **Verification:** `go test ./pkg/picod/... -run TestAuthMiddleware_ClockLeeway -v` 通过；覆盖 delta-spec §Scenario: Clock leeway tolerates minor skew\n89: \n90: ---\n91: \n92: ## T6. 线程安全验证\n93: \n94: - [ ] 6.1 测试 `TestAuthManager_ConcurrentReads`：多个 goroutine 同时调用 AuthMiddleware → 无死锁\n95: - [ ] 6.2 测试 `TestAuthManager_ConcurrentReadWrite`：一个 goroutine 调用 LoadPublicKeyFromEnv 的同时，其他 goroutine 调用 AuthMiddleware → 无数据竞争\n96: \n97: **Verification:** `go test -race ./pkg/picod/... -run TestAuthManager_Concurrent -v` 无数据竞争警告；覆盖 delta-spec §Requirement: Thread-safe public key access\n98: \n99: ---\n100: \n101: ## T7. 代码质量门禁\n102: \n103: - [ ] 7.1 运行 `go build ./pkg/picod/...` 确认编译通过\n104: - [ ] 7.2 运行 `go test ./pkg/picod/... -v -count=1` 确认全部测试通过\n105: - [ ] 7.3 运行 `go test -race ./pkg/picod/...` 确认无数据竞争\n106: - [ ] 7.4 运行 `go vet ./pkg/picod/...` 确认无警告\n107: - [ ] 7.5 确认代码中无 `log.Printf` 使用（仅使用 `klog`）\n108: - [ ] 7.6 确认错误响应中不泄露 JWT token 或密钥材料\n109: \n110: **Verification:** 所有门禁命令 exit code 0；无敏感数据出现在日志或错误响应中\n111: \n112: ---\n113: \n114: ## Task Dependencies\n115: \n116: ```\n117: T1\n118: │\n119: T2 ── T3 ── T4\n120:       │     │\n121:       T5    T6\n122:       │     │\n123:       └─────┴── T7\n124: ```\n125: \n126: **Parallel execution:**\n127: - T2 和 T3 可并行开发（T2 定义结构体和方法签名后，T3 即可开始实现中间件逻辑）\n128: - T5（leeway 测试）可与 T4 并行\n129: - T6（并发测试）需 T2 和 T3 完成后开始\n130: - T7 为最终门禁，需所有前置任务完成\n131: \n132: ---\n133: \n134: ## Acceptance Criteria\n135: \n136: | # | Criterion | Command |\n137: |---|-----------|---------|\n138: | AC1 | 编译通过 | `go build ./pkg/picod/...` |\n139: | AC2 | 全部测试通过 | `go test ./pkg/picod/... -v -count=1` |\n140: | AC3 | 无竞态条件 | `go test -race ./pkg/picod/...` |\n141: | AC4 | 无 lint 警告 | `go vet ./pkg/picod/...` |\n142: | AC5 | AuthManager 公钥加载覆盖 4 个场景（有效/缺失/无效PEM/非RSA） | `go test ./pkg/picod/... -run TestAuthManager_LoadPublicKeyFromEnv -v` |\n143: | AC6 | AuthMiddleware 覆盖 7 个场景（缺失header/格式错误/有效/过期/非RSA/MaxBody/leeway） | `go test ./pkg/picod/... -run TestAuthMiddleware -v` |\n144: | AC7 | Server 路由保护验证（/health 公开，/api 需认证） | `go test ./pkg/picod/... -run TestServer -v` |\n145: | AC8 | 线程安全验证（并发读、并发读写无竞争） | `go test -race ./pkg/picod/... -run TestAuthManager_Concurrent -v` |\n146: | AC9 | 无 `log.Printf` 使用 | `grep -r 'log\\.Printf' pkg/picod/` 无输出 |\n147: | AC10 | 错误响应不泄露敏感信息 | 审查 auth.go 中所有 401 响应体 |\n\n(End of file - total 147 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-017 — PicoD JWT 中间件 — Tasks\n\n> **Module:** pkg/picod\n> **Language:** Go\n> **Size:** S\n> **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n> **Reference:** `changes/AR-017/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-017/design.md`, `changes/AR-017/delta-spec.md`\n\n## T1. 定义认证常量和类型\n\n- [ ] 1.1 在 `pkg/picod/types.go` 中定义常量 `PublicKeyEnvVar = \"PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY\"`\n- [ ] 1.2 在 `pkg/picod/types.go` 中定义常量 `MaxBodySize = 32 << 20`（33554432，即 32 MiB）\n- [ ] 1.3 运行 `go build ./pkg/picod/...` 确认编译通过\n\n**Verification:** 常量值与 delta-spec §Requirement: Constants and configuration 一致；编译零错误\n\n---\n\n## T2. 实现 AuthManager 结构体和公钥加载\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-017/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775848522206,"end":1775848522211}}}}
